<br>
Anyway, I pulled continuously to 2 Earth, 1 Air, 1 Water, and one Epic pet. After Epic had agro, chanter would slow, mob would die. Every now and then we would nuke for fun, but noone except chanter ever went below 90m. Chanter stayed at a fairly constant 60m which would have been higher if he had a horse. <br>
<br>
Overall the xp was amazing! Pets spread out damage, only one normally needing heal was Epic. I've grouped with conventional groups in PoN alot recently trying to hit 55, and I've never seen mobs die as quickly as they did with this combo. Only real down time was during bio breaks.<br>
<br>
We did lose one mage a few times, I believe due to overnuke, but pulling continued with only 4 pets with no problems.<br>
<br>
